## 10. Glossary

**Melee:** One event (bracket, ballot, pool, etc.)  
**Group:** Named friend circle for a Melee  
**Stage:** Discrete unit (round, category, etc.)  
**Contender:** Option available within a Stage  
**Picks:** User selections  
**Outcome:** Actual event winner/result  
**Chatter:** Group live feed (comments, reactions)  
**Activity Feed:** Log of all picks and changes  
**Prop Question:** Tie-breaker & engagement device  
**Spectator:** Read-only invitee  
**Host:** User who creates a Melee

